# Accident Detection System

## Overview
This project detects accidents using MPU6050 sensor and sends alert using GSM module.

## Components Used
- STM32 / Arduino
- MPU6050 Sensor
- GSM Module

## Working
- Detects sudden movement
- Sends alert message

